{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-404-crisscross-ellipses","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Izazov 404: Elipsa koja raste","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>$E_a$ je elipsa čija je jednačina oblika $x^2 + 4y^2 = 4a^2$.</p>\n<p>$E_a'$ je rotacija od $E_a$ za ugao $\\theta$, u smeru suprotnom kazaljci, oko porekla $O(0, 0)$ za $0° &#x3C; θ &#x3C; 90°$.</p>\n<img alt=\"ellipse E_a and ellipse rotated by θ degrees E_a'\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/crisscross-ellipses.gif\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>$b$ je udaljenost od početka dve presečne tačke koje su najbliže početku, a $c$ je udaljenost između dve druge presečne tačke.</p>\n<p>Naziva se poređani triplet ($a$, $b$, $c$) za standardni elipsoidni triplet ako su $a$, $b$ i $c$ pozitivni ceo brojevi.</p>\n<p>Na primer, (209, 247, 286) je standardni elipsoidni triplet.</p>\n<p>Neka $C(N)$ bude broj različitih trojki standardnih elipsoida ($a$, $b$, $c$) za $a \\leq N$.</p>\n<p>Može se dokazati da $C({10}^3) = 7$, $C({10}^4) = 106$ i $C({10}^6) = 11\\,845$.</p>\n<p>Pronađi $C({10}^{17})$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f5001000cf542c510012","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302072,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-404-crisscross-ellipses"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function crisscrossEllipses() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\ncrisscrossEllipses();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>crisscrossEllipses()</code> treba da vrati <code>1199215615081353</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(crisscrossEllipses(), 1199215615081353);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-401-to-480","dashedName":"problem-404-crisscross-ellipses","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-405-a-rectangular-tiling","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-403-lattice-points-enclosed-by-parabola-and-line","id":"5900f5001000cf542c510012","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-404-crisscross-ellipses"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}